  "active_lock_reason": null,
  "body": "Hi all,\r\n\r\nCurrently, validator does not attempt to restart its main workflow if it disconnects from a running beacon node. Thus, the beacon node sleeping can lead to issues similar to what Danny encountered in #622. If gRPC disconnects or we encounter some sort of fatal error, the validator should attempt to reset and start again from scratch as if it just connected to a beacon node. A PR for this would resolve the problem and work correctly at runtime.\r\n\r\n",
